              <a class="launch-slide-link" href="https://www.producthunt.com/products/burnlink?embed=true&amp;utm_source=badge-featured&amp;utm_medium=badge&amp;utm_campaign=badge-burnlink-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                Open on Product Hunt
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="launch-slide-item">
              <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="launch-slide-copy">Support the launch with your vote and feedback</span>
              <span class="launch-slide-sep" aria-hidden="true">•</span>
              <span class="launch-slide-copy">Privacy-first. Browser-encrypted. Ephemeral by design</span>
              <span class="launch-slide-sep" aria-hidden="true">•</span>
              <a class="launch-slide-link" href="https://www.producthunt.com/products/burnlink?embed=true&amp;utm_source=badge-featured&amp;utm_medium=badge&amp;utm_campaign=badge-burnlink-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                Visit Product Hunt
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="launch-slide-item" aria-hidden="true">
              <span class="dot"></span>
              <span class="launch-slide-copy">BurnLink is now live on Product Hunt</span>
              <span class="launch-slide-sep">•</span>
              <span class="launch-slide-copy">Encrypted file sharing with one-time burn links</span>
              <span class="launch-slide-sep">•</span>
              <a class="launch-slide-link" href="https://www.producthunt.com/products/burnlink?embed=true&amp;utm_source=badge-featured&amp;utm_medium=badge&amp;utm_campaign=badge-burnlink-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" tabindex="-1">
                Open on Product Hunt
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="launch-slide-item" aria-hidden="true">
              <span class="dot"></span>
              <span class="launch-slide-copy">Support the launch with your vote and feedback</span>
              <span class="launch-slide-sep">•</span>
              <span class="launch-slide-copy">Privacy-first. Browser-encrypted. Ephemeral by design</span>
              <span class="launch-slide-sep">•</span>
              <a class="launch-slide-link" href="https://www.producthunt.com/products/burnlink?embed=true&amp;utm_source=badge-featured&amp;utm_medium=badge&amp;utm_campaign=badge-burnlink-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" tabindex="-1">
                Visit Product Hunt
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h1>The file link that<br><em>burns itself.</em></h1>
        <p>Encrypted in your browser. Delivered once. Permanently deleted on access. No accounts, no logs, no trace.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <h2>Why BurnLink?</h2>
          <p>Most file-sharing tools store your file indefinitely and log who accessed it. BurnLink is built on the opposite principle.</p>
          <div class="feature-rows">
            <div class="feature-row"><span class="fr-dot"></span><span class="fr-text">AES-256-GCM encryption — key never leaves your browser</span></div>
            <div class="feature-row"><span class="fr-dot"></span><span class="fr-text">Link is cryptographically burned after first access</span></div>
            <div class="feature-row"><span class="fr-dot"></span><span class="fr-text">View-once mode with 60-second in-browser timer</span></div>
            <div class="feature-row"><span class="fr-dot"></span><span class="fr-text">Optional password — independent key derivation layer</span></div>
            <div class="feature-row"><span class="fr-dot"></span><span class="fr-text">No account, no email, no IP logs &mdash; <a href="https://github.com/Joy-Majumder/BurnLink" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color:#eb583d;text-decoration:none;">open source</a></span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="upload-section">
          <h2>Upload a file</h2>
          <% if (error) { %>
            <p class="error-msg"><%= error %></p>
          <% } %>
          <form id="upload-form" method="post" action="/upload" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="file">Select file</label>
              <input type="file" id="file" name="file" required />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="password">Password (optional)</label>
              <div class="password-input-wrap">
                <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="Leave empty for link-only access" pattern="\S*" title="Passwords cannot contain spaces." />
                <button id="password-toggle" class="password-toggle" type="button" aria-label="Show password" aria-pressed="false">Show</button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label>Share mode</label>
              <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem;">
                <label style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; cursor: pointer; flex: 1;">
                  <input type="radio" name="mode" value="view-once" checked required style="width: 16px; height: 16px;" />
                  <span style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #aaa;">View once</span>
                </label>
                <label style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; cursor: pointer; flex: 1;">
                  <input type="radio" name="mode" value="download" required style="width: 16px; height: 16px;" />
                  <span style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #aaa;">Download file</span>
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>
            <button id="upload-btn" type="submit">Encrypt &amp; Upload</button>
            <span id="upload-status" class="status" aria-live="polite"></span>
          </form>
          <div id="link-box" class="link-box" hidden>
            <strong>Your secure link</strong>
            <a id="share-link" href="#"></a>
            <div class="link-actions">
              <button id="copy-link-btn" type="button">Copy link</button>
              <span id="copy-status" class="status" aria-live="polite"></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

